{"tid":1550441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 究竟我地要點先贏","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:51:00.000Z","uid":163271,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"569fcdfd5b9928a4d95e6ed11f0bc11c6adb0ac8","tid":1550441,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:59.000Z","msg":"坐定定un un街等老美過法案得啦仲打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申 非大台</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d58daa6bf543893a22042e2f5c9674e0de5af2","tid":1550441,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a069f5dbd8671ea54c46773f2df9483426fe18aa","tid":1550441,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1952ca3d9b8bb8849600f98fa97b0cba7cb76379","tid":1550441,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"If we burn, you burn with us."},{"pid":"39c7b17a50